spective advertisers or partners regarding product or service usage on IIL network is provided in an aggregate form only and does not include any personally identifiable information about any individual user. Users may log in to <a href=\"http://my.indiamart.com/\">http://my.Vardhaman Textile.com/</a> to check current status of their contact sharing permissions.\r\n\r\nWe request our users to sign out of their IIL account and close their browser window when they have finished their work. This is to ensure that others cannot access their personal or business information and correspondence, if the user shares the computer with someone else or is using a computer in a public place.\r\n\r\nIIL takes necessary steps, within its limits of commercial viability and necessity, to ensure that the user\'s information is treated securely.\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, no data transmission over the Internet can be guaranteed to be 100% secure. As a result, while IIL strives to protect the user\'s personal &amp; business information, it cannot ensure the security of any information transmitted to IIL and you do so at your own risk. Once IIL receives your transmission, it makes best efforts to ensure its security in its systems. Please keep in mind that whenever you post personal &amp; business information online, that is accessible to the public, you may receive unsolicited messages from other parties.\r\n\r\n<strong>Changes in Privacy Policy</strong>\r\nThe policy may change from time to time so please check periodically.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Privacy Policy','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision-v1','','','2014-11-09 07:02:50','2014-11-09 07:02:50','',11,'http://192.168.1.33/wordpress/?p=12',0,'revision','',0),(17,1,'2014-11-09 07:24:42','2014-11-09 07:24:42','Vardhaman Textile India Pvt. Ltd is a merchandise selling site. This firm was established long back in 1999, Since then it has grown a lot. Our shop started by selling Bedsheet and now we sell almost all un-stiched merchandise.\n\